#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Purpose of the &atlantik; board game is to acquire land in major cities in "
"North America and Europe while being a transatlantic traveler. To win the "
"game, players improve monopolized land with profitable buildings in the "
"hopes of bankrupting all other players."
msgstr ""
"Namen namizne igre &atlantik; je pridobivanje zemljišč v večjih mestih v "
"Severni Ameriki in Evropi, medtem ko ste čezatlantski popotnik. Za zmago v "
"igri igralci izboljšajo monopolno zemljišče z donosnimi zgradbami v upanju, "
"da bodo vsi drugi igralci bankrotirali."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All game modes are served by &monopd;, a dedicated game server designed for "
"&atlantik;. One of the game modes plays like the popular real estate board "
"game known as &Monopoly;."
msgstr ""
"Vse načine igre streže &monopd;, namenski strežnik za igre, zasnovan za "
"&atlantik;. Eden od načinov igre se igra kot priljubljena nepremičninska "
"družabna igra, znana kot &Monopoly;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Connecting to a Server"
msgstr "Povezovanje s strežnikom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&atlantik; requires a game server to connect to. If you have an Internet "
"connection, you can request a list of public Internet servers and you will "
"not require additional software. If you want to play &atlantik; locally, on "
"a <acronym>LAN</acronym> or on a private Internet server, you can enter the "
"hostname and port to connect to. In this case, you will need the <ulink url="
"\"https://gtkatlantic.gradator.net/\">&monopd;</ulink> server software "
"installed and running on the host you are connecting to."
msgstr ""
"&atlantik; za povezavo potrebujete igralni strežnik. Če imate internetno "
"povezavo, lahko zahtevate seznam javnih internetnih strežnikov in ne boste "
"potrebovali dodatne programske opreme. Če želite igrati &atlantik; lokalno, "
"v <acronym>LAN</acronym> ali na zasebnem internetnem strežniku, lahko "
"vnesete ime gostitelja in vrata za povezavo. V tem primeru boste potrebovali "
"strežniško programsko opremo <ulink url=\"https://gtkatlantic.gradator.net/"
"\">&monopd;</ulink> nameščeno in zagnano na gostitelju, s katerim se "
"povezujete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have problems connecting to a server, the following troubleshoot "
"notes might help you:"
msgstr ""
"Če imate težave pri povezovanju s strežnikom, vam bodo morda pomagale "
"naslednje opombe za odpravljanje težav:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Try another server."
msgstr "Poskusi z drugim strežnikom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check your firewall and masquerading settings. Restrictions might be in "
"place preventing you from connecting to servers or receiving reply traffic. "
"By default, &monopd; servers use TCP port 1234. If you are not sure, contact "
"your system administrator."
msgstr ""
"Preverite vdorobran in nastavitve maskiranja. Morda obstajajo omejitve, ki "
"vam preprečujejo povezavo s strežniki ali prejemanje odgovorov. Privzeto je, "
"da &monopd; strežniki uporabljajo vrata TCP 1234. Če niste prepričani, se "
"obrnite na skrbnika sistema."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Menubar"
msgstr "Menijska vrstica"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Game Menu"
msgstr "Meni igre"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Event Log…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži dnevnik dogodkov…</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Display</action> the event log window."
msgstr "<action>Prikaži</action> okno dnevnika dogodkov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reconnect (After Crash)</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ponovna povezava (po sesutju)</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Reconnect</action> to the last game. This is available only in case "
"&atlantik; did not quit cleanly from a game (usually because it crashed), "
"and cannot be done anymore once you connect to a server."
msgstr ""
"<action>Ponovna povezava</action> z zadnjo igro. To je na voljo samo če "
"&atlantik; ni čisto zapustil igre (običajno zato, ker se je sesula) in tega "
"ni več mogoče storiti, ko se povežete s strežnikom."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Leave Game</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zapusti igro</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Leave the current game</action>, without closing &atlantik;."
msgstr "<action>Zapusti trenutno igro</action>, ne da bi zaprl &atlantik;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Close</action> &atlantik;."
msgstr "<action>Zapri</action> &atlantik;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Move Menu"
msgstr "Meni Premakni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>End Turn</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Premik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Končaj potezo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Let the other players know you have finished moving."
msgstr "Sporočite drugim igralcem, da ste končali premikanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>Roll Dice</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu><guimenuitem>Meči kocko</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Roll the dice."
msgstr "Vrzi kocko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>Auction</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dražba</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start an auction."
msgstr "Začnite dražbo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>Use Card to Leave Jail</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Premakni se</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uporabi kartico za odhod iz "
"zapora</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use a card to leave jail."
msgstr "Uporabi kartico za odhod iz zapora."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>Roll to Leave Jail</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu><guimenuitem>Meči, da zapustiš zapor</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Roll the dice to leave the jail."
msgstr "Vrzite kocko, da zapustite zapor."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings and Help Menus"
msgstr "Meniji Nastavitve in Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&atlantik; has the the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menus described in the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html\">Menu</ulink> chapter of the &kde; Fundamentals "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"&atlantik; ima skupni &kde; meni <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> in "
"<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> sta opisana v poglavju <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html\">Meni</ulink> v &kde; Dokumentacija o osnovah."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reporting Bugs"
msgstr "Poročanje o napakah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you think you have found a bug in &atlantik;, please report it. "
"Developers often catch and fix bugs themselves, but you might experience "
"issues not yet known. Not reporting your problems might very well prevent "
"them from being fixed indefinitely."
msgstr ""
"Če menite, da ste našli napako v &atlantik;, jo prijavite. Razvijalci "
"pogosto sami odkrijejo in odpravijo hrošče, vendar lahko naletite na težave, "
"ki še niso znane. Če ne poročate o svojih težavah, lahko preprečite, da bi "
"jih popravili za nedoločen čas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can report bugs for &atlantik; at the <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org/"
"\">&kde; Bug Tracking System</ulink>. Use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Report Bug…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to "
"visit the bug wizard with some details of your &atlantik; version filled in "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Lahko prijavite napake za &atlantik; na <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org/"
"\">&kde; Sistem za sledenje napakam</ulink>. Uporabite element menija "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prijavi napako…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da obiščete čarovnika za napake z nekaterimi "
"podrobnostmi vašega &atlantik; različica se izpolni samodejno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please specify details in your bug report, such as game conditions. For "
"example, a bug might only occur when people are in jail, or during an "
"auction. If possible, save the event log and attach it to the bug report or "
"send it to the author. It might contain vital clues about behavior that "
"could lead to a faster resolution for the bug."
msgstr ""
"V poročilu o napakah navedite podrobnosti, kot so pogoji igre. Na primer, "
"napaka se lahko pojavi le, ko so ljudje v zaporu ali med dražbo. Če je "
"mogoče, shranite dnevnik dogodkov in ga priložite poročilu o napakah ali pa "
"ga pošljite avtorju. Morda vsebuje bistvene namige o vedenju, ki bi lahko "
"vodilo do hitrejše rešitve napake."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Answers to Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "Odgovori na pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I add a computer player?"
msgstr "Kako dodam računalniškega igralca?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unfortunately, computer opponents are not yet supported by &atlantik;."
msgstr "Na žalost &atlantik; še ne podpira računalniških nasprotnikov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Users are advised to take advantage of the public Internet servers or a "
"private <acronym>LAN</acronym> server."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnikom svetujemo, da izkoristijo prednosti javnih internetnih "
"strežnikov ali zasebnega <acronym>LAN</acronym> strežnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I trade?"
msgstr "Kako naj trgujem?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on a player portfolio or estate with the &RMB; and you can open a "
"trade."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite portfelj ali posestvo igralca z &RMB; in lahko odprete trgovino."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are a two usability issues with trades that can cause confusion. If "
"you in any way include another player in a trade, that player will get the "
"trade window. Any player can reject the terms, which unnecessarily ends the "
"trade session for all other players as well. A trade has to be accepted by "
"all players in it before it can completed, which can be complicated because "
"players remain a participant in deals even when they are no longer involved "
"with tradeable items."
msgstr ""
"Obstajata dve težavi z uporabnostjo trgovanja, ki lahko povzročita zmedo. Če "
"na kakršen koli način v trgovanje vključite drugega igralca, bo ta igralec "
"dobil okno za trgovanje. Vsak igralec lahko pogoje zavrne, kar po "
"nepotrebnem konča trgovalno sejo tudi za vse ostale igralce. Trgovanje "
"morajo sprejeti vsi igralci v njem, preden se lahko zaključi, kar je lahko "
"zapleteno, ker igralci ostanejo udeleženci v poslih, tudi če niso več "
"vključeni v predmete, s katerimi se trguje."

